import org.apache.spark.ml.Pipeline
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.{RandomForestClassifier}
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature._
import org.apache.spark.sql.{Row, SQLContext}


    //build model
    val pathToWikiCategotyToArticleTermsMapping = "file:///home/ipertushin/IdeaProjects/pornocluster/data/wiki/mapping-as-obj/extract"
    val categoryToTermsMappingDF = sc.objectFile[(String, Seq[String])](pathToWikiCategotyToArticleTermsMapping)
        .toDF("category", "terms")
        
    categoryToTermsMappingDF.registerTempTable("WikiCategotyToArticleTermsMapping")
      
    val pathToPdmlData = "file:///home/ipertushin/IdeaProjects/pornocluster/data/pdml-html-payload-terms/extract"  
    val pdmlDataTermsDF =  sc.objectFile[Seq[String]](pathToPdmlData)
    .map(s => (s.hashCode, s))
    .toDF("id", "terms")
        
    pdmlDataTermsDF.registerTempTable("PdmlDataTerms")
        
        
    val categoryToLabelIndexer = new StringIndexer()
      .setInputCol("category")
      .setOutputCol("label")

    val hashingTF = new HashingTF()
      .setNumFeatures(1000)
      .setInputCol("terms")
      .setOutputCol("tfFeatures")

    val idf = new IDF()
      .setInputCol("tfFeatures")
      .setOutputCol("tfidfFeatures")

    val normalizer = new Normalizer()
      .setInputCol("tfidfFeatures")
      .setOutputCol("normalizedFeatures")

    val scaller = new StandardScaler()
      .setInputCol("normalizedFeatures")
      .setOutputCol("scaledFeatures")

    val rf = new RandomForestClassifier()
      .setNumTrees(3)
      .setFeatureSubsetStrategy("auto")
      .setImpurity("gini")
      .setMaxDepth(5)
      .setMaxBins(32)
      .setFeaturesCol("scaledFeatures")
       //.setMaxMemoryInMB(4000)


    val pipeline = new Pipeline()
      .setStages(
            Array(
                categoryToLabelIndexer,
                hashingTF,
                idf,
                normalizer,
                scaller,
                rf
            )
      )

    // Fit the pipeline to training documents.
    val model = pipeline.fit(categoryToTermsMappingDF)

    val test = pdmlDataTermsDF.select("terms")

    // Make predictions on test documents.
    model.transform(test)
      .select("terms","prediction")
      .registerTempTable("ResultPredictions")

import org.apache.spark.ml.Pipeline
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.RandomForestClassifier
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature._
import org.apache.spark.sql.{Row, SQLContext}

val categories = sqlContext.sql("select category from WikiCategotyToArticleTermsMapping")

val categoryToLabelIndexer = new StringIndexer()
      .setInputCol("category")
      .setOutputCol("label")

categoryToLabelIndexer.fit(categories).transform(categories)
      .registerTempTable("CategoryToLabelMapping")

%sql 

select m.category, count(rp.prediction) as predictedTimes
    from ResultPredictions rp, 
         CategoryToLabelMapping m
    where rp.prediction = m.label
    group by m.category
    order by predictedTimes desc
